    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>游戏内容：</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过收集各色各样的卡牌帮助我们的女妖穿过危险重重的妖精之地！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18个关卡，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多个风情各异的女妖， </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6个种族的卡牌， </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200多张卡牌！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 主英雄携带专属的爆衣系统！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085070/extras/6dcef661f2aa5a4c63bdb27805fcb89a.poster.avif?t=1751852023\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085070/extras/6dcef661f2aa5a4c63bdb27805fcb89a.webm?t=1751852023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085070/extras/6dcef661f2aa5a4c63bdb27805fcb89a.mp4?t=1751852023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤多种属性小怪的<strong>妖王</strong>！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085070/extras/0fc5afd7add153b2e566ff61b4c3c94c.poster.avif?t=1751852023\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085070/extras/0fc5afd7add153b2e566ff61b4c3c94c.webm?t=1751852023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085070/extras/0fc5afd7add153b2e566ff61b4c3c94c.mp4?t=1751852023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul